<span id="freeTextContainer2346939931377605370">“...Rufino had learned over the years that emotions came not from the heart, but from the soul. And he certainly still had one of those.”<br/><br/>Rufino is a vampire, has been for 6 years, and learned early on that it is an isolated existence. Bartenders seem to be his only acquaintances, but if he wants to stay alive (kind of), it has to be that way. There are some people in Nyobi that don&apos;t take too kindly to vampires...they do drink blood (and whisky in Rufino&apos;s case) after all. <br/><br/>In this great piece of</span>
