<div id="review_4531286912" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/4531286912" />
    <a title="Gary" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/147316683-gary"><img alt="Gary" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1644101452p2/147316683.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/4531286912?book_show_action=true">Feb 05, 2022</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Gary" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Gary" href="/user/show/147316683-gary">Gary</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="did not like it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">did not like it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer4531286912" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer15002461593720698779">The author is an anti-vaxxer, so it&apos;s no wonder he&apos;s a fiction writer. Unfortunately his lack of awareness mirrors his imaginative ability, with a story that slowly treads from one cliché to the next. While this book may be a slog, it at least works as an effective sleeping pill. </span>
  <span id="freeText15002461593720698779" style="display:none">The author is an anti-vaxxer, so it's no wonder he's a fiction writer. Unfortunately his lack of awareness mirrors his imaginative ability, with a story that slowly treads from one cliché to the next. While this book may be a slog, it at least works as an effective sleeping pill. </span>
  <a data-text-id="15002461593720698779" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


      <div class="reviewFooter uitext buttons">
          

